;RUSHING RIVER (Holodeck Program)
NUMBER 3482
NAME Rushing River
REGION 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777

CALL 49

RELOGIN 1920
EXIT BELOW 3483

ITEM 0 1312 ADJ1=145
