ITEM 0 403 ADJ1=1225 ADJ2=355
ITEM 1 1125 ADJ1=355
ITEM 2 198 ADJ1=441 VAL2=100
ITEM 3 1667
ITEM 4 1108 ADJ1=355 VAL2=3482
ITEM 5 1312

*DESCRIPTION_START
The sounds of rushing water assault your hearing as your senses try to take in
the surrounding scene. In the near total darkness, you are barely able to make
out lumbering shapes swimming in the murky waters below. Through the hazy mist
you can see the dim glow of the lanterns back on the deck.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
From its position on the far side of the wooden deck, the raft is protected
from most of the roughness of the rushing river. You notice that it is tethered
to the deck by a strong rope, which is a good thing, since it would undoubtably
be swept down stream into the darkness of the unknown if it were not. 
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
You notice a wooden ladder leading back up to the top of the deck.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
In the darkness you can see large shapes swimming through the murky water.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB TOUCH 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You dangle your fingers in %a.
   ECHO OTHERS %N dangles %h fingers in %a.
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
   IFVAR DUMMY1 > 2
      ECHO PLAYER You feel something bump against your fingers, and quickly snatch them away!
      ECHO OTHERS %N gasps and quickly snatches %h fingers away from the water.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 2
