;
;SECRET THICKET (Holodeck Program)
NUMBER 3486
NAME Secret Thicket
REGION 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777

CALL 49

RELOGIN 1920
EXIT BELOW 3485

ITEM 0 1557
ITEM 1 376 ADJ1=298 ADJ2=135
EXTEND 1 of fallen pine needles
PUT 1 1484 ADJ1=25
ITEM 2 664 ADJ1=297
ITEM 3 1232
EXTEND 3 laden with juicy red berries
PUT 3 493 ADJ1=750 ADJ2=259 VAL2=2 VAL5=9
ITEM 4 411 ADJ1=308

*DESCRIPTION_START
You feel a thick mat of soft pine needles cushioning your knees as your eyes
slowly adjust to the dim light in this warm, dry hideaway. The low ceiling,
allowing just enough room to kneel, is an impenetrable mass of intertwining
smooth wooded vines. A silver leafed berry bush protects the thicket from the
wind, the sound of the summer storm still raging on outside. All you feel is a
warm breeze drifting in through the leafy opening.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Through the opening you see brief flashes from the raging thunderstorm.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GAZE 0
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You peer out the leafy opening and into the pouring rain.
   ECHO OTHERS %N peers out into the rain.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 0
   ECHO PLAYER Perhaps you should try ducking out the opening.
   CLEARVERB
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The ground cover mat consists of dried pine needles and soft feathery leaves
from the berry bush.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB TOUCH 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The natural mattress of soft fragrant needles is dry and inviting.
   ECHO OTHERS %N rests %h hand on the soft needles, pressing down a few times with a pleased smile on %s lips.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
Soft green stems spport a lattice of smooth, green, heart-shaped leaves.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB TOUCH 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The smooth wood feels just slightly damp, a few drops of water sliding downwards to bump against your
finger.
   ECHO OTHERS As %N touches the vines, they shift slightly sending a few escaped drops of water plummeting to the
floor.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
It is bushy and dense with aromatic leaves, its thin branches laden with red
juicy berries.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
Its just a regular old rock with a flat top, a perfect little picnic table.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB DUCK -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You crawl out of the leafy opening.
   ECHO OTHERS %N ducks through the leafy opening.
   DISBAND
   MOVE 3485
   AFFECT 3485
   ECHO OTHERS %N crawls out through the leafy opening.
   POSITION STAND
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
   IFVAR ARCHNUM = -1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You hear the splatter of heavy rain hitting the leaves outside.
      ECHO PLAYER %N tilts %h head to one side to listen.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You inhale deeply, detecting the aromatic spice from the leaves of the berry
   ECHO PLAYER bush on a background of a warm musty wet forest smell.
   ECHO OTHERS %N deeply inhales the pure mountain air.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GET -1
   IFVAR ARCHNUM = 493
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You remove a juicy red berry from the bush.
      ECHO OTHERS %N removes a juicy red berry from the bush.
      NEWITEM -1 493 ADJ1=750 ADJ2=259 VAL2=2 VAL5=9
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB STAND -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER There is no room to stand up here.
ENDIF

IFSAY LEAVE_PROGRAM
   IFVAR PLRSINROOM < 2
      ECHO PLAYER A soft voice from nowhere in tones, "You are on the only inhabitant of this
      ECHO PLAYER holodeck program. To leave, please say END PROGRAM and then exit the holodeck.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR PLRSINROOM > 1
      ECHO PLAYER A swirling light begins to surround you. When it fades, you find you are no
      ECHO PLAYER longer where you were before...
      ECHO OTHERS A swirling light begins to surround %N. When it fades, %s is no longer there.
      MOVE 1920
      AFFECT 1920
      ECHO OTHERS You hear a low hum, and then %N appears surrounded by a swirling light that soon fades.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFSAY END_PROGRAM
   ECHO ALL The scene fades instantly away...
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   EQUAL EXIT 3485
   CALL 38
ENDIF
