   IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You step out of the pond onto a flat smooth boulder.
      ECHO OTHERS %N steps out of the pond.
      EQUAL FLAG1 0
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The huge tree is open and spreading, with pointed heart-shaped leaves that
are bright green above and silvery green below. The tree blooms in this 
perpetual summer with tiny fragrant yellow blossoms.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH 3
   IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
      ECHO PLAYER You can't reach that from in the pond.
