*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
Its lush green ferns sprout out in several directions, surrounding the pond.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH 4
   IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You can't reach that from where you are.
   ENDIF
