*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
You see a slightly fleshy plant, with long spiney leaves, growing from a
single center. Toward the top of the plant the new leafs are scarlet, and in
their midst is a cluster of tiny nondescript blossoms.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH 5
   IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You can't reach that from where you are.
